                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4947Treatise">Treatise for the feast of the baptism of Our Lord Jesus Christ</title>
                        <incipit>
                           በስመ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">አብ፡</supplied> 
